<p>I</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">śubhamastu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ādicaṇdheśvara je</hi>ya<hi rend="grantha">m <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakābdam śrī</hi>nāḷ parākkirama pāṇṭiya tevaṟku yāṇṭu 5 vatu kīlaka varu<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>m Āvaṇi mācam <hi rend="grantha"><num value="17"><g type="numeral">10</g> 7</num>§ <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> </hi>
