<p>II</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/>Uruttiravīṇai vīraiyaṟku <hi rend="grantha">Aśva</hi>tināḷ <hi rend="grantha">jā</hi>taṉāṉa naṅkumāraṉ tirunelveli perumāḷ nam koyilil <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> vatukku tiruvāḻiyāka kaṟpittu vara viṭukaiyil Ōlaippaṭi kuṭukkak kaṟpitta koṭṭūr nāṭṭu kāmantatevaṉ muṉ Āḷai <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
</p>

